{
  "stem": "54.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we didn't know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Nobody knew because we didn't go out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We didn't know what's going on outside of the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were in a different world, you know, just selected from everyone and-- and, you know, isolated from everybody.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And around the-- we had fences around, electrical fences, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Couldn't go-- you couldn't get, you know, close to the fence because you-- you were afraid you were going to be electrocuted.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day, we noticed some-- some of the guys, you know, were walking around, they were around the fence, and they told us they couldn't talk to us because they were not allowed to talk to us.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two guys came around the fence, and they said to us, don't you-- didn't you notice that the light is not anymore every night on like it used to be before?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We said, what do we know what's going on outside the world?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were like the sheep-- like the sheeps there in the-- in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said, you be-- you just watch out, watch and be outside-- more outside the barracks, that you should get some information.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know then-- then you will know what's going on outside the world.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One day, we noticed that we didn't get any food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quite a few days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't cook.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans start, you know, running away from the camp, the one who was with us inside.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because knew what's going-- they had the papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had the news from radio.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we didn't have nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they start running away because they were afraid that the American will come in, they'll be in big trouble.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So one day, I said-- we had the girls from our camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
